
<h2>Philosophy</h2>

<hr>

<p>
Micrantha aims to be a conscious<sub><a href="#conscious">1</a></sub> business.</p>

<p>
We do not seek to claim or impose an identity.  We aim to fulfill a shared purpose<sub><a href="#purpose">2</a></sub>.
</p>

<p>
We aim to work from a state of acceptance, enthusiasm or enjoyment.
</p>

<p>Our results form naturally and inherently, and our failures deepen us.
</p>

<p>
An analogy to the software development we do is gardening and we grow our creations.
</p>

